{Could SOUTH bid 2\H, (FSF), even though she actually has the suit?

Perhaps, but there is no reason to do so. NORTH does not have four \Hs 
or he would have mentioned them before bidding \Ss.

SOUTH should ignore the \H suit and bid 3NT.}

